#: ../../source/chain/rgb.rst:6 32bf2ec56dfa4329b62d911de6bd9499
msgid ""
"RGBChain is the helper class for Chain RGB display devices on the Chain "
"bus. It provides methods to control an 8 x 8 RGB display using RGB888 "
"integer color values, including pixel drawing, full-screen buffer "
"refresh, ASCII character display, scrolling text, brightness, and "
"rotation."
msgstr ""
"RGBChain 是 Chain 总线上 Chain RGB 显示设备的辅助类。它提供控制 8x8 RGB 显示屏的方法，使用 RGB888 "
"整数颜色值，支持像素绘制、全屏缓冲区刷新、ASCII 字符显示、滚动文本、亮度和旋转。"

